# âœ… Project Title: **Lawyer-Client Legal Services Web App**

---

## ðŸ”¹ 1. Project Summary

The Lawyer-Client Web App is a secure, cloud-based platform that facilitates communication, case management, and legal service delivery between lawyers and their clients. It allows users to manage legal matters, share documents, communicate in real-time, schedule appointments, and handle billingâ€”all within a single application.

---

## ðŸ”¹ 2. Goals

* Streamline legal service delivery
* Enable secure and efficient lawyer-client communication
* Provide case transparency to clients
* Offer easy access to legal documents and records
* Reduce manual paperwork and administrative overhead

---

## ðŸ”¹ 3. User Roles

### ðŸ”¸ 1. **Lawyer**

* Manages client cases
* Communicates with clients
* Uploads documents
* Tracks appointments and billing

### ðŸ”¸ 2. **Client**

* Requests legal help
* Views case progress
* Uploads documents
* Schedules meetings and pays invoices

---

## ðŸ”¹ 4. Core Features

### ðŸ”¸ Authentication & User Management

* Secure registration/login (JWT or OAuth)
* Role-based access (Lawyer vs. Client)
* Password reset and profile management

### ðŸ”¸ Case Management

* Create, assign, and update cases
* Attach documents to cases
* Case status tracking (Open, In Progress, Closed)

### ðŸ”¸ Document Management

* Upload/download files
* Version control and file access tracking
* Shared document folders per case

### ðŸ”¸ Messaging & Chat

* Real-time chat between lawyer and client
* Message threads organized by case
* Email notifications for unread messages

### ðŸ”¸ Appointments & Scheduling

* Calendar integration
* Schedule and reschedule meetings
* Automated reminders via email/SMS

### ðŸ”¸ Invoicing & Payment

* Generate and send invoices
* Clients can pay online (Stripe, PayPal)
* Payment history and invoice tracking

### ðŸ”¸ Notifications

* In-app, email, and optional SMS notifications
* Notification center in dashboard
* Customizable alert preferences

### ðŸ”¸ Admin Panel (Optional for Firms)

* Manage users, lawyers, and analytics
* System-wide settings and logs

---

## ðŸ”¹ 5. Optional Features

* Video conferencing (Zoom/Google Meet integration)
* E-signatures (DocuSign/HelloSign)
* AI chatbot for FAQs or legal form assistance
* Mobile app or PWA for on-the-go access

