## ðŸ”¹ 6. Technology Stack (Suggested)

### ðŸ”¸ Frontend

* **React.js / Vue.js / Next.js**
* Responsive UI (Bootstrap, Tailwind CSS)
* WebSocket for real-time chat

### ðŸ”¸ Backend

* **Node.js (Express) / Django / Laravel**
